title: FBI takes down alert on chip credit cards after bankers complain
text:
12 FBI takes down alert on chip credit cards after bankers complain 
Networkworld: The FBI posted an online advisory about vulnerabilities with new chip-enabled credit cards, but then removed the message on Friday, less than a day later, following concerns from U.S. bankers that back chip cards.
